Package: modPackage
Title: Workflow tools to allow for modular R package development
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Luke", "Duttweiler", , "lduttweiler@hsph.harvard.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0467-995X"))
Description: This package contains workflow tools that allow for the development of R packages that use multi-level directory organization of code. This is currently avery simple development version. Will be expanded. 
